moji\" /> )<br />\n諗諗下其實響景點擺pose會有紀念性多d但係唔夠膽響外面做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\njojo pose<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/06/185217_6be22a63c3027b12d33b73ba1025c63b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F06%2F185217_6be22a63c3027b12d33b73ba1025c63b.png&h=d2e0657a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f12e25bd7184f5b527bd28fb6b24c61e8dbba47","tid":654962,"uid":87780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T10:53:24.000Z","msg":"儲一套銀仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39728edf5b6594433de74c820c566b59b13af5ce","tid":654962,"uid":40042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a7e14014651a0bb131ceefe61ec81eb7875dc8e","tid":654962,"uid":158228,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T10:52:46.000Z","msg":"響酒店同bf對著塊鏡擺jojo pose自拍 ( 我知好撚奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n諗諗下其實響景點擺pose會有紀念性多d但係唔夠膽響外面做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\njojo pose<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/06/185217_6be22a63c3027b12d33b73ba1025c63b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F06%2F185217_6be22a63c3027b12d33b73ba1025c63b.png&h=d2e0657a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T12:13:43.000Z","msg":"曾經有個女性購友每次去到啲景點，<br />\n都要男朋友托起佢隻大腳，然後攬住佢，<br />\n影啲唔乎合人體工學嘅pose相，拍得住jojo任何一個pose <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果時條女仲話以後去邊度旅行都要影呢啲相<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n不過佢地後來分左手"},{"pid":"d4e8ff809e3bf4f9b608370f8d44a832251d2b35","tid":654962,"uid":108502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T12:24:27.000Z","m